tool_description: An API showing most of Lithuanian jokes from Lithuanian internet. Has few  endpoints to return all, random, and all by searchable word/phrase.
name: Lithuanian Jokes
title: Lithuanian Jokes

api_list.name: Get Jokes Filtered by desired word
api_list.description: Show all joke containing searchable word

api_list.name: Get Random Lithuanian Joke
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://lithuanian-jokes.p.rapidapi.com/random"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "lithuanian-jokes.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
